{"tid":2226384,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"駐港5年 愛爾蘭記者麥固崙（Aaron McNicholas）被拒續簽證","createTime":"2020-10-02T04:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T05:31:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ca6a808efce757e710c9a3b6aeb3b925762d4d","tid":2226384,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:25:52.000Z","msg":"在港居住5年的愛爾蘭記者麥固崙（Aaron McNicholas），周四在愛爾蘭網上媒體撰文指接獲香港入境處通知，其簽證續期被拒，惟對方未有解釋原因。<br />\n<br />\n麥固崙過去5年一直在港居住，為美國、愛爾蘭及英國等多個主要媒體，報道香港最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，自己已於本周初離開香港，又慨嘆自《港區國安法》生效後，本港的新聞自由正面對日益嚴峻挑戰，擔憂記者會否成為下一個被針對的目標。<br />\n<br />\nTODAY, 1 OCTOBER is a public holiday in Hong Kong, as it is throughout China, ostensibly to celebrate the country&rsquo;s National Day.<br />\n<br />\nAn occasion that is traditionally marked with a showcase fireworks display has been tempered this year by the Covid-19 pandemic, meaning that no mass gathering is allowed to take place.<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s also the first National Day in five years that I will not be spending in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nAfter living and working as a journalist in the city since 2015, I left earlier this week following the Hong Kong government&rsquo;s decision to decline my visa renewal application.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thejournal.ie/readme/hong-kong-democracy-5219310-Oct2020/?utm_source=shortlink\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejournal.ie%2Freadme%2Fhong-kong-democracy-5219310-Oct2020%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshortlink&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdApktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=c19975f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thejournal.ie/readme/hong-kong-democracy-5219310-Oct2020/?utm_source=shortlink</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1311558737619017730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1311558737619017730&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdApktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=61c9daf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1311558737619017730&h=c9c51cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1311558737619017730</a>"},{"pid":"72e931af1877fd2a84e334ad4ecbb352593c4fcc","tid":2226384,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a609db57e68d2a8130056b765e8dce6664e7ba17","tid":2226384,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整咗條咁嘅片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2224648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8685845f21e8ab77b0bb8d7fe839d0db63caf66","tid":2226384,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72e931af1877fd2a84e334ad4ecbb352593c4fcc","tid":2226384,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳喎.....喎......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ef3c86995c248da26b6ae279b79014aa21447","tid":2226384,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"港豬：<br />\n<br />\n太負面啦<br />\n<br />\n香港需要正面記者"},{"pid":"f7852829384613f4f02cfd3237ec31d7efe4127f","tid":2226384,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8685845f21e8ab77b0bb8d7fe839d0db63caf66","tid":2226384,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72e931af1877fd2a84e334ad4ecbb352593c4fcc","tid":2226384,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳喎.....喎......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited